      <div type="edition" xml:lang="mi-Latn">
	<p>
	  <lb n="1"/>
	  sidhaṃ kumārasa 
	  <persName key="pers:Viṣṇupālita">kāṇabhoasa
	    vheṇupālitasa</persName>
	  <lb n="2"/>
	  <unclear>e</unclear>sa leṇa cetieghara ovarakā ca
	  aṭha 8 vi kmaṃ niyu<lb n="3" break="no"/>taṃ 
	  le<supplied reason="omitted">ṇ</supplied>sa ca 
	  ubhato pasesu poḍhiyo be 2 leṇasa
	  <lb n="4"/>
	  āligaṇake patho ca dato etasa ca
	  kumārasa deya
	</p>
      </div>
      <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
	<p>
	  Success! Prince <persName key="pers:Viṣṇupālita">Kāṇabhoja Viṣṇupālita’s</persName> cave, caitya, and eight (8) cells. This much work is endowed, and two (2) cisterns on each side of the cave, also a passage connected with the cave are presented. It is a charitable gift of that prince.
	</p>
      </div>
